textBeforeTable: Playlist Tracks:  Former local boy Willie Wisely phones in from Los Angeles to talk (pop) shop with Liberty Finch and DJ Izzy. Hear cuts from his latest release, "True," plus Willie's picks, including Jimmy Reed, Bobby "Blue" Bland, Le Fleur de Lys, Small Faces, the Corner Laughers and more. Plus, a musical tribute to Donald "Duck" Dunn. DJ Izzy Liberty Finch DJs:  May 15, 2012 The Pop Shop Program:    5/15/2012 The Pop Shop
